<lb n="2" break="no"/>cuntaracoḻa pāṇṭiyatevaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="21">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 1</num>
<lb n="3"/>ki<unclear>ḻi</unclear>raṇiyamuṭṭattu mel veṇ Iraṇṇiya
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṉ colai tiruvāṉaimalaiymel Eḻuntaruḷiya <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>naraciṅkatevarkku vaicca vi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷakkukku vacca Āḷākku ne<supplied reason="omitted">y</supplied>kku vaicca Āṭu <num value="25">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 5</num> Ittevar veṭṭikkuṭi nakkaṉ ceṇ
<lb n="6" break="no"/>pakatteṉ Ivvāṭu <num value="25">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 5</num> koṇṭu Ittevarkku ca<hi rend="grantha">ntrā</hi>tittaval muṭṭāma laṭṭuva
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tāṉeṉ nakkaṉ ceṇpatteṉ nāṉum Eṉ vaṟkattārum muṭṭāmalaṭṭuvatāṉe
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṉ <g type="ddanda">.</g><g type="dashLong">.</g>
